 /url: /paulg\n                                  - generic [ref=e376]:\n                                    - generic [ref=e378]: Paul Graham\n                                    - img [ref=e381]\n                                - generic [ref=e385]:\n                                  - link [ref=e387]:\n                                    - /url: /paulg\n                                    - generic [ref=e388]: \"@paulg\"\n                                  - generic [ref=e389]: ·\n                                  - link [ref=e391]:\n                                    - /url: /paulg/status/2028342817727426732\n                                    - time [ref=e392]: 35m\n                              - generic [ref=e394]:\n                                - button [ref=e396]:\n                                  - img [ref=e401]\n                                - button [ref=e407]:\n                                  - img [ref=e411]\n                            - generic [ref=e415]: Amjad showed me Replit's latest stuff. They're about to redefine vibe coding in a way that will seem obvious in retrospect. A lot of the biggest ideas have that quality.\n                            - group [ref=e418]:\n                              - button [ref=e420]:\n                                - generic [ref=e421]:\n                                  - img [ref=e424]\n                                  - generic [ref=e429]: \"47\"\n                              - button [ref=e431]:\n                                - generic [ref=e432]:\n                                  - img [ref=e435]\n                                  - generic [ref=e440]: \"10\"\n                              - button [ref=e442]:\n                                - generic [ref=e443]:\n                                  - img [ref=e446]\n                                  - generic [ref=e449]:\n                                    - generic [ref=e451]: \"385\"\n                                    - generic [ref=e453]: \"386\"\n                              - link [ref=e455]:\n                                - /url: /paulg/status/2028342817727426732/analytics\n                                - generic [ref=e456]:\n                                  - img [ref=e459]\n                                  - generic [ref=e464]: 19K\n                              - button [ref=e466]:\n                                - img [ref=e470]\n                              - button [ref=e475]:\n                                - img [ref=e479]\n                      - article [ref=e485] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - generic [ref=e491]:\n                          - link [ref=e503]:\n                            - /url: /paulg\n                          - generic [ref=e507]:\n                            - generic [ref=e509]:\n                              - generic [ref=e512]:\n                                - link [ref=e515]:\n                                  - /url: /paulg\n                                  - generic [ref=e516]:\n                                    - generic [ref=e518]: Paul Graham\n                                    - img [ref=e521]\n                                - generic [ref=e525]:\n                                  - link [ref=e527]:\n                                    - /url: /paulg\n                                    - generic [ref=e528]: \"@paulg\"\n                                  - generic [ref=e529]: ·\n                                  - link [ref=e531]:\n                                    - /url: /paulg/status/2028262400714277057\n                                    - time [ref=e532]: 5h\n                              - generic [ref=e534]:\n                                - button [ref=e536]:\n                                  - img [ref=e541]\n                                - button [ref=e547]:\n                                  - img [ref=e551]\n                            - generic [ref=e555]: One thing we do in office hours is cook up bold long-term plans to tell investors about to convince them that the startup has at least some chance of being huge. But often as not these then become the startup's actual plan.\n                            - group [ref=e558]:\n                              - button [ref=e560]:\n                                - generic [ref=e561]:\n                                  - img [ref=e564]\n                                  - generic [ref=e569]: \"41\"\n                              - button [ref=e571]:\n                                - generic [ref=e572]:\n                                  - img [ref=e575]\n                                  - generic [ref=e580]: \"10\"\n                              - button [ref=e582]:\n                                - generic [ref=e583]:\n                                  - img [ref=e586]\n                                  - generic [ref=e591]: \"431\"\n                              - link [ref=e593]:\n                                - /url: /paulg/status/2028262400714277057/analytics\n                                - generic [ref=e594]:\n                                  - img [ref=e597]\n                                  - generic [ref=e602]: 39K\n                              - button [ref=e604]:\n                                - img [ref=e608]\n                              - button [ref=e613]:\n                                - img [ref=e617]\n                      - article [ref=e623] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - generic [ref=e631]:\n                          - link [ref=e643]:\n                            - /url: /paulg\n                          - generic [ref=e647]:\n                            - generic [ref=e649]:\n                              - generic [ref=e652]:\n                                - link [ref=e655]:\n                                  - /url: /paulg\n                                  - generic [ref=e656]:\n                                    - generic [ref=e658]: Paul Graham\n                