ideo 0:00 of 1:03 Play 0:00 / 1:04 Show captions Unmute 100 percent Video Settings Picture-in-Picture Full screen 205 replies, 962 reposts, 5327 likes, 6963 bookmarks, 509231 views\" [ref=e48]:\n      - article \"Andrew Ng Verified account @AndrewYNg Feb 25 Impressive inference speed from Inception Labs’ diffusion LLMs. Diffusion LLMs are a fascinating alternative to conventional autoregressive LLMs. Well done @StefanoErmon and team! Quote Stefano Ermon Verified account @StefanoErmon Feb 24 Mercury 2 is live 🚀 🚀 The world’s first reasoning diffusion LLM, delivering 5x faster performance than leading speed-optimized LLMs. Watching the team turn years of research into a real product never gets old, and I’m incredibly proud of what we’ve built. We’re just getting Show more Embedded video Play Video 75 replies, 157 reposts, 1405 likes, 515 bookmarks, 173628 views\" [ref=e49]:\n      - article \"Andrew Ng Verified account @AndrewYNg Feb 23 Will AI create new job opportunities? My daughter Nova loves cats, and her favorite color is yellow. For her 7th birthday, we got a cat-themed cake in yellow by first using Gemini’s Nano Banana to design it, and then asking a baker to create it using delicious sponge cake and Image 114 replies, 101 reposts, 756 likes, 227 bookmarks, 89736 views\" [ref=e50]:\n      - 'article \"Andrew Ng Verified account @AndrewYNg Feb 14 To all my AI friends: Every time I see you, you raise my temperature parameter. Happy Valentine’s Day! ❤️ 113 replies, 106 reposts, 1989 likes, 71 bookmarks, 116106 views\"':\n      - article \"Andrew Ng Verified account @AndrewYNg Feb 13 I recently spoke at the Sundance Film Festival on a panel about AI. Sundance is an annual gathering of filmmakers and movie buffs that serves as the premier showcase for independent films in the United States. Knowing that many people in Hollywood are extremely uncomfortable Image 76 replies, 33 reposts, 228 likes, 42 bookmarks, 40391 views\" [ref=e51]:\n      - heading \"Who to follow\" [ref=e52] [level=2]\n      - button \"Paul Graham and 2 others follow Geoffrey Hinton Verified account @geoffreyhinton Follow @geoffreyhinton deep learning\" [ref=e53]:\n      - button \"Google DeepMind Verified account @GoogleDeepMind Follow @GoogleDeepMind We’re a team of scientists, engineers, ethicists and more, committed to solving intelligence, to advance science and benefit humanity.\" [ref=e54]:\n      - button \"DeepLearning.AI Verified account @DeepLearningAI Follow @DeepLearningAI We are an education technology company with the mission to grow and connect the global AI community.\" [ref=e55]:\n      - link \"Show more\" [ref=e56]:\n      - 'article \"Andrew Ng Verified account @AndrewYNg Feb 12 New course: A2A: The Agent2Agent Protocol, built with @googlecloudtech and @IBMResearch , and taught by Holt Skinner, @ivnardini , and Sandi Besen. Connecting agents built with different frameworks usually requires extensive custom integration. This short course teaches you A2A, Embedded video Play Video 76 replies, 92 reposts, 621 likes, 457 bookmarks, 77141 views\"':\n    - search \"Search\":\n      - combobox \"Search query\" [ref=e57]\n    - complementary \"Who to follow\":\n      - heading \"You might like\" [ref=e58] [level=2]\n      - list:\n      - link \"Show more\" [ref=e59] [nth=1]:\n    - region \"Trending now\" [ref=e60]:\n      - heading \"Trending now\" [ref=e61] [level=1]\n      - heading \"What’s happening\" [ref=e62] [level=2]\n      - link \"Trending in Albania Albanians More\" [ref=e63]:\n      - link \"Politics · Trending Kosovo More\" [ref=e64]:\n      - link \"Politics · Trending Serbia More\" [ref=e65]:\n      - link \"Politics · Trending Ukraine More\" [ref=e66]:\n      - link \"Show more\" [ref=e67] [nth=2]:\n    - navigation \"Footer\" [ref=e68]:\n      - link \"Terms of Service\" [ref=e69]:\n      - text: \"|\"\n      - link \"Privacy Policy\" [ref=e70]:\n      - text: \"|\"\n      - link \"Cookie Policy\" [ref=e71]:\n      - text: \