t of 165 replies, 102 reposts, 2607 likes, 590 bookmarks, 194884 views\" [ref=e48]:\n      - 'article \"Ian Goodfellow Verified account @goodfellow_ian Nov 18, 2025 Amazing test of Gemini 3’s multimodal reasoning capabilities: try generating a threejs voxel art scene using only an image as input Prompt: I have provided an image. Code a beautiful voxel art scene inspired by this image. Write threejs code as a single-page Embedded video Play Video 91 replies, 320 reposts, 2946 likes, 1206 bookmarks, 426187 views\"':\n      - article \"Ian Goodfellow Verified account @goodfellow_ian Nov 18, 2025 Try it for yourself at aistudio.google.com/apps/bundled/i Embedded video Play Video 6 replies, 8 reposts, 140 likes, 76 bookmarks, 25578 views\" [ref=e49]:\n      - article \"Ian Goodfellow Verified account @goodfellow_ian Nov 18, 2025 Replying to @goodfellow_ian Best outputs from Gemini 2.5 Pro, vs 3 Pro, this example nicely illustrates the fidelity jump with 3 Pro, through strong multimodal understanding and 3D reasoning Embedded video Play Video Play Embedded video Play Video Play 4 replies, 13 reposts, 153 likes, 24 bookmarks, 18470 views\" [ref=e50]:\n      - article \"Ian Goodfellow Verified account @goodfellow_ian Oct 16, 2025 More of what my colleagues and I have been working on in AI for fusion is public now Quote Square profile picture Google DeepMind Verified account @GoogleDeepMind Oct 16, 2025 We’re announcing a research collaboration with @CFS_energy, one of the world’s leading nuclear fusion companies. Together, we’re helping speed up the development of clean, safe, limitless fusion power with AI. ⚛️ Image 57 replies, 136 reposts, 2817 likes, 447 bookmarks, 285236 views\" [ref=e51]:\n      - article \"Ian Goodfellow reposted Yoshua Bengio Verified account @Yoshua_Bengio Oct 15, 2025 AI is evolving too quickly for an annual report to suffice. To help policymakers keep pace, we're introducing the first Key Update to the International AI Safety Report. 🧵 ⬇️ (1/10) h