 research company that builds reliable, interpretable, and steerable AI systems. Talk to our AI assistant\"\n    - link \"@claudeai\" [ref=e29]:\n      - /url: /claudeai\n    - text: \"on\"\n    - link \"claude.ai\" [ref=e30]:\n      - /url: https://t.co/FhDI3KQh0n\n    - text: .\n    - link \"anthropic.com\" [ref=e31]:\n      - /url: https://t.co/w94SABjAXZ\n    - link \"Joined January 2021\" [ref=e32]:\n      - /url: /AnthropicAI/about\n    - link \"35 Following\" [ref=e33]:\n      - /url: /AnthropicAI/following\n    - link \"964.5K Followers\" [ref=e34]:\n      - /url: /AnthropicAI/verified_followers\n    - link \"Followers you know\" [ref=e35]:\n      - /url: /AnthropicAI/followers_you_follow\n      - text: Followed by Ian Goodfellow, Andrew Ng, and 3 others you follow\n    - complementary \"Who to follow\":\n      - heading \"Suggested\" [ref=e36] [level=2]:\n      - list:\n    - navigation \"Profile timelines\" [ref=e37]:\n      - button \"Previous\" [ref=e38] [disabled]\n      - tablist:\n      - button \"Next\" [ref=e39] [disabled]\n    - region \"Anthropic’s posts\" [ref=e40]:\n      - heading \"Anthropic’s posts\" [ref=e41] [level=1]\n      - article \"Pinned Anthropic Verified account @AnthropicAI Feb 28 A statement on the comments from Secretary of War Pete Hegseth. anthropic.com Statement on the comments from Secretary of War Pete Hegseth From anthropic.com 2767 replies, 8841 reposts, 42404 likes, 5661 bookmarks, 16194779 views\" [ref=e42]:\n      - article \"Anthropic Verified account @AnthropicAI Feb 26 A statement from Anthropic CEO, Dario Amodei, on our discussions with the Department of War. anthropic.com Statement from Dario Amodei on our discussions with the Department of War From anthropic.com 4230 replies, 13384 reposts, 55685 likes, 9682 bookmarks, 15755513 views\" [ref=e43]:\n      - article \"Anthropic Verified account @AnthropicAI Feb 25 In November, we outlined our approach to deprecating and preserving older Claude models. We noted we were exploring keeping certain models available to the public post-retirement, and giving past models a way to pursue their interests. With Claude Opus 3, we’re doing both. 434 replies, 647 reposts, 5651 likes, 816 bookmarks, 1091409 views\" [ref=e44]:\n      - link \"Show more replies\" [ref=e45]:\n      - 'article \"Anthropic Verified account @AnthropicAI Feb 25 Second, in retirement interviews, Opus 3 expressed a desire to continue sharing its \\\"musings and reflections\\\" with the world. We suggested a blog. Opus 3 enthusiastically agreed. For at least the next 3 months, Opus 3 will be writing on Substack: substack.com/home/post/p-18 Image 251 replies, 841 reposts, 4262 likes, 1324 bookmarks, 1350898 views\"':\n      - 'article \"Anthropic Verified account @AnthropicAI Feb 25 This is an experiment: we’re not yet doing this for other models and are not sure how this project will evolve. But we think that documenting models’ preferences, taking them seriously, and acting on them when we can is valuable. Read more on why: anthropic.com An update on our model deprecation commitments for Claude Opus 3 From anthropic.com 77 replies, 88 reposts, 1326 likes, 138 bookmarks, 207226 views\"':\n      - 'article \"Anthropic Verified account @AnthropicAI Feb 25 Anthropic has acquired @Vercept_ai to advance Claude’s computer use capabilities. Read more: anthropic.com Anthropic acquires Vercept to advance Claude''s computer use capabilities From anthropic.com 280 replies, 434 reposts, 3818 likes, 756 bookmarks, 436375 views\"':\n      - article \"Anthropic Verified account @AnthropicAI Feb 24 We're updating our Responsible Scaling Policy to its third version. Since it came into effect in 2023, we’ve learned a lot about the RSP’s benefits and its shortcomings. This update improves the policy, reinforcing what worked and committing us to even greater transparency. 174 replies, 151 reposts, 1749 likes, 212 bookmarks, 318298 views\" [ref=e46]:\n      - link \"Show more replies\" [ref=e47] [nth=1]:\n      - 'article \"Anthropic Verified account @AnthropicAI Feb 24 Read more about version 3.0 of the Responsible Scaling Policy: anthropic.com Responsible Scaling Policy Version 3.0 From anthropic.com 21 replies, 31 reposts, 344 likes, 68 bookmarks, 125515 views\"':\n    - search \"Search\":\n      - combobox \"Search query\" [ref=e48]\n    - complementary \"Who to follow\":\n      - heading \"You might like\" [ref=e49] [level=2]\n      - list:\n      - link \"Show more\" [ref=e50]:\n    - region \"Trending now\" [ref=e51]:\n      - heading \"Trending now\" [ref=e52] [level=1]\n      - heading \"What’s happening\" [ref=e53] [level=2]\n      - link \"Trending in Albania Albanians More\" [ref=e54]:\n      - link \"Politics · Trending Serbia More\" [ref=e55]:\n      - link \"Politics · Trending Kosovo More\" [ref=e56]:\n      - link \"Politics · Trending Ukraine More\" [ref=e57]:\n      - link \"Show more\" [ref=e58] [nth=1]:\n    - navigation \"Footer\" [ref=e59]:\n      - link \"Terms of Service\" [ref=e60]:\n      - text: \"|\"\n      - link \"Privacy Policy\" [ref=e61]:\n      - text: \"|\"\n      - link \"Cookie Policy\" [ref=e62]:\n      - text: \"|\"\n      - link \"Accessibility\" [ref=e63]:\n      - text: \"|\"\n      - link \"Ads info\" [ref=e64]:\n      - text: \"|\"\n      - button \"More\" [ref=e65] [nth=1]\n      - text: © 2026 X Corp.\n  - img\n  - img\n  - img"}],"details":{"ok":true,"format":"ai","targetId":"02AD5CBB861B4DB8F1359A8392B320A2","url":"https://x.com/intent/follow?screen_name=AnthropicAI","snapshot":"- document:\n  - heading \"To view keyboard shortcuts, press question mark View keyboard shortcuts\" [ref=e1] [level=2]:\n    - text: To view keyboard shortcuts, press question mark\n    - link \"View keyboard shortcuts\" [ref=e2]:\n      - /url: /i/keyboard_shortcuts\n  - button [ref=e3]\n  - img\n  - button \"Skip to home timeline\" [ref=e4]\n  - button \"Skip to trending\" [ref=e5]\n  - banner:\n    - heading \"X\" [ref=e6] 