{"type":"message","id":"77035bb6","parentId":"134b08a1","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:17:22.209Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9f3d002615c64f7985fdbca7","toolName":"browser","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  - heading \"To view keyboard shortcuts, press question mark View keyboard shortcuts\" [ref=e1] [level=2]:\n    - text: To view keyboard shortcuts, press question mark\n    - link \"View keyboard shortcuts\" [ref=e2]:\n      - /url: /i/keyboard_shortcuts\n  - button [ref=e3]\n  - button \"Skip to home timeline\" [ref=e4]\n  - button \"Skip to trending\" [ref=e5]\n  - banner:\n    - heading \"X\" [ref=e6] [level=1]:\n      - link \"X\" [ref=e7]:\n    - navigation \"Primary\" [ref=e8]:\n      - link \"Home\" [ref=e9]:\n      - link \"Search and explore\" [ref=e10]:\n      - link \"Notifications\" [ref=e11]:\n      - link \"Follow\" [ref=e12]:\n      - link \"Direct Messages\" [ref=e13]:\n      - link \"Grok\" [ref=e14]:\n      - link \"Bookmarks\" [ref=e15]:\n      - link \"Creator Studio\" [ref=e16]:\n      - link \"Premium\" [ref=e17]:\n      - link \"Profile\" [ref=e18]:\n      - button \"More menu items\" [ref=e19]\n    - link \"Post\" [ref=e20]:\n      - /url: /compose/post\n    - button \"Account menu\" [ref=e21]:\n  - main:\n    - button \"Back\" [ref=e22]\n    - heading \"Scale AI Verified account\" [ref=e23] [level=2]:\n      - text: Scale AI\n    - text: 2,224 posts\n    - button \"Search\" [ref=e24]\n    - link \"Square profile picture and Opens profile photo\" [ref=e25]:\n      - /url: /scale_AI/photo\n    - button \"More\" [ref=e26]\n    - button \"Turn on post notifications\" [ref=e27]\n    - button \"Following @scale_AI\" [ref=e28]: Unfollow\n    - text: Scale AI\n    - button \"Provides details about verified accounts.\" [ref=e29]:\n    - text: \"@scale_AI making AI work\"\n    - link \"scale.com\" [ref=e30]:\n      - /url: https://t.co/ECE0dHmBSO\n    - link \"Joined July 2016\" [ref=e31]:\n      - /url: /scale_AI/about\n    - link \"482 Following\" [ref=e32]:\n      - /url: /scale_AI/following\n    - link \"73.3K Followers\" [ref=e33]:\n      - /url: /scale_AI/verified_followers\n    - text: Not followed by anyone you’re following\n    - complementary \"Who to follow\":\n      - heading \"Suggested\" [ref=e34] [level=2]:\n    - navigation \"Profile timelines\" [ref=e35]:\n      - button \"Previous\" [ref=e36] [disabled]\n      - button \"Next\" [ref=e37] [disabled]\n    - region \"Scale AI’s posts\" [ref=e38]:\n      - heading \"Scale AI’s posts\" [ref=e39] [level=1]\n      - article \"Scale AI reposted Jason Droege Verified account @jdroege Feb 27 AI agents are getting put to work on real tasks. Training them to do that well is harder than it looks. For the past year at @scale_AI , we've been building environments where agents can practice real workflows - simulated worlds that mirror real software, real processes, and scale.com Scaling Intelligence with RL Environments From scale.com 2 replies, 9 reposts, 26 likes, 5 bookmarks, 2350 views\" [ref=e40]:\n      - article \"Scale AI reposted Bing Liu Verified account @vbingliu Feb 25 Congrats to the @OpenAI team for topping the Audio MultiChallenge speech-to-speech (S2S) leaderboard with the latest gpt-realtime-1.5 release. Audio MultiChallenge (Audio MC) is a benchmark released by @scale_AI to evaluate how end-to-end speech models handle real-world, Quote Peter Bakkum Verified account @pbbakkum Feb 25 gpt-realtime-1.5 is the best native audio model on the Scale AudioMultiChallenge benchmark -- this is a significant jump in capability by this measure. There are models that outperform it but they are reasoning models without native audio output. Image 2 replies, 7 reposts, 49 likes, 4 bookmarks, 12350 views\" [ref=e41]:\n      - article \"Scale AI Verified account @scale_AI Feb 24 Honored to see SWE-Bench Pro recognized as the new standard for frontier coding evals. 💜 We built it to address saturation and contamination in earlier benchmarks — raising the bar with a more rigorous measure of agents' problem-solving capabilities and a clearer view of Quote Square profile picture OpenAI Developers Verified account @OpenAIDevs Feb 23 The standard for frontier coding evals is changing with model maturity. We now recommend reporting SWE-bench Pro and are sharing more detail on why we’re no longer reporting SWE-bench Verified as we work with the industry to establish stronger coding eval standards. SWE-bench Show more 6 replies, 9 reposts, 38 likes, 4 bookmarks, 4686 views\" [ref=e42]:\n      - article \"Scale AI Verified account @scale_AI Feb 20 Lots of new models have shipped recently. 👀 When the conversation turns from “what launched” to “how they perform,” the reference points are our leaderboards. Here’s a recap of the latest models evaluated ⬇️ 5 replies, 4 reposts, 18 likes, 2 bookmarks, 3634 views\" [ref=e43]:\n      - link \"Show more replies\" [ref=e44]:\n      - article \"Scale AI reposted Sam Denton @samueldenton Feb 17 2026 is the year agents learn when to ask for help Our research from @scale_AI introduces Long Horizon Augmented Workflows (LHAW), a synthetic data generation pipeline for creating underspecification on ANY dataset (yes, you can try this at home!) and evaluating how agents act 🧵 Image 4 replies, 12 reposts, 77 likes, 61 bookmarks, 7762 views\" [ref=e45]:\n    - search \"Search\":\n      - combobox \"Search query\" [ref=e46]\n    - complementary \"Who to follow\":\n      - heading \"You might like\" [ref=e47] [level=2]\n      - link \"Show more\" [ref=e48]:\n    - region \"Trending now\" [ref=e49]:\n      - heading \"Trending now\" [ref=e50] [level=1]\n      - heading \"What’s happening\" [ref=e51] [level=2]\n      - link \"Trending in Albania Albanians More\" [ref=e52]:\n      - link \"Politics · Trending Kosovo More\" [ref=e53]:\n      - link \"Politics · Trending Serbia More\" [ref=e54]:\n      - link \"Show more\" [ref=e55] [nth=1]:\n    - navigation \"Footer\" [ref=e56]:\n      